  "general_provisions": "This bill creates requirements for holding certain municipal or county offices.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>provides that a state executive branch official or a county official may not serve on a municipal legislative body, subject to a time-limited exception;<hr><ltbullet>provides that a state executive branch official or a municipal official may not serve on a county legislative body, subject to a time-limited exception;<hr><ltbullet>includes a sunset provision; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
